<t>
<field>YIELD.TO.MAT</field>
<desc>
            <p>This field will display a Yield for the value dated security transaction based upon the general formula of; </p>
            <p>CONSID. = CF1/(1+r) + CF2/(1+r)**2 + etc + CFn/(1+r)**n </p>
            <p>Where; r = Yield CFn = Income during period n n = number of days since trade divided by number of days in year. </p>
            <p>The yield will then be found by iteration. </p>
            <p>
                <p>Validation Rules:</p>
            </p>
            <p>No input field.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
